I would have been fine with walking a quarter of a mile back but no, we had to walk a whole mile back, bare footed on a hot board walk, in 101 degree weather. You would think that's all? Nope, not whatsoever. They took parts of the beach they didn't even need and didn't tell us to move in a nice way. You would thing they'd say "will you please move.", nonono, they said "We need this part of the beach so move down and don't come over or you'll be detained."
